{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Generously grease 6 Thermomix® ramekins size 1.","Place oat biscuits and butter in mixing bowl then chop <b>15 sec\/speed 5<b>. Divide mixture between prepared ramekins and press down evenly with fingers or back of a spoon.","Place cream cheese, quark, 60 g caster sugar, vanilla sugar, flour and egg in mixing bowl then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 4<b>. Divide mixture between prepared ramekins, pouring over biscuit bases. Cover each ramekin with heat-resistant cling film and place in Varoma dish. Clean mixing bowl.","Place mango, remaining 20-30 g caster sugar and lemon juice in mixing bowl then blend <b>20 sec\/speed 7<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside. Clean mixing bowl.","Place water in mixing bowl, place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove Varoma, carefully remove ramekins and leave to cool completely.","Remove cling film, spoon reserved mango purée over cheesecakes and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["70 g oat biscuits, coated with chocolate, broken in pieces","20 g unsalted butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","200 g cream cheese","150 g quark (curd cheese)","80 - 90 g caster sugar","10 g vanilla sugar","2 tsp plain flour (10 g)","1 medium egg","200 g frozen mango, defrosted","1 - 2 tsp lemon juice, to taste","500 g water"]}],"id":"r365606","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-yzGAWPV-O5o\/XZWchfXCyAI\/AAAAAAAAea4\/e6XNv7LAe9oBHNE301EWxeYkvMBaQZzswCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_0K3k_GngPMPJcRvC.png","title":"Mini Cheesecakes with Mango Purée","publishedAt":"2018-10-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9 g","fat":"19 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"30 g","calories":"1394 kJ \/ 333 kcal"},"usefulItems":"heat-resistant cling film","hintsAndTricks":["Adjust quantities of sugar and lemon juice in purée according to sweetness of mango and personal preference.","Cheesecakes can be prepared a day in advance. Refrigerate overnight and finish with mango purée just before serving."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","3h","6 portions"]}